ludes 4 Afro Asian Games gold medals and 6 medals at the Asian games and 2 medals at the Common wealth Games. Sania was conferred with the Arjuna Award as a result of her immense and constant achievements. Sania has helped the cause of development of womens sport tremendously. Sania was appointed as the Governments representative to the Save the girl child initiative.","can_post":false,"category":"Athlete","checkins":0,"cover":{"cover_id":953641154665514,"offset_x":0,"offset_y":100,"source":"https:\/\/scontent.xx.fbcdn.net\/hphotos-xft1\/t31.0-8\/s720x720\/10857348_953641154665514_1112606357840706706_o.png","id":"953641154665514"},"has_added_app":false,"is_community_page":false,"is_published":true,"likes":8502090,"link":"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/sania.mirza","name":"Sania Mirza","parking":{"lot":0,"street":0,"valet":0},"personal_info":"https:\/\/twitter.com\/MirzaSania\n\nhttp:\/\/www.cornerstone.in\/portfolio_4\/sania-mirza\/","talking_about_count":528959,"username":"sania.mirza","were_here_count":0}